data.description:
Let this property work for you! SINGLE-FAMILY home zoned live/work. Upstairs there are 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full baths, an extra large covered balcony and tons of upgrades; This home shows like a model. Downstairs there is 800+ square feet of commercial/retail and 2- two car garages (4 car garage total (total 700+ sf). The downstairs can be used to run your business (major tax advantages) or can be leased out to a commercial tenant $$$. It also works well as an incredible ADA accessible mother in law suite, multi- generational space, or bonus entertainment space. Lower level includes a large full bath and kitchenette.Don't miss out on this rare find in Abacoa. Windsor Park in Abacoa is a pristine neighborhood. Amenities include  resort style pool, fitness gym, entertainment room, meeting room, catering kitchen, fire pit, open spaces, walking trails, dog park, ect. 

Easy access to I-95 and turnpike, 3.5 miles to beach, world renowned golf courses, 5 star restaurants, A rated schools, 20 minutes to airport and downtown West Palm.
